About us

About Deyhaat

DeyHaat develops & operates Solar Pico-grids  in rural India offering Affordable, Reliable & CLEAN energy as-a-service to last mile lowest income generating Micro-enterprises & underserved communities.We are accelerating the usage of  Renewable Energy while replacing Kerosene lamps & Diesel generators.
DeyHaat is creating a significant social impact by addressing the challange of  Energy Access, which in-turn is helping to improve livelihoods & uplifting socio-economic status of vulnerable communities.CLEAN power through Solar helps to reduce carbon emissions while creating a safe & cleaner environment for all.

what we do

Community Pico-Grids|EFC|O&M|Last Mile Distribution

⦿ We develop & operate solar Pico-grids offering Clean, Reliable & Affordable Energy access for underserved communities.

⦿ We offer customized solution from Engineering design, procurement & installation for solar power plants focusing C&I sector.

⦿ We manage operation & maintenance service for utility and rooftop solar power plants along with performance monitoring.

﻿⦿ We promote & distribute renewable energy products in rural regions through external partners under "DeyHaat Saathi" initiative.
